{"title":"北国短笛（组诗）","authors":["王忠范"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":6,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"北国短笛（组诗）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王忠范"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿伦河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兴安岭扯出的一行诗句"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"描绘北中国的名字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管天空与阳光很边远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成片的农业绿了古老的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑土地涌现着夏天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲一句长长的叮咛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晶莹成从不枯竭的力量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日与夜曲曲弯弯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可呼喊的希望滚滚向前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们便是一朵朵浪花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在兴安岭下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在红鸡冠之上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏牧场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏牧场是一面旗帜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥动着羊群与蹄声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平铺的日子长满绿茵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百灵鸟朗诵着广阔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鞭花溅成露珠溅成牧歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏天在白云里柔软和芬芳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏牧场被羊群移动着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在古神树的那边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羊角号呼唤着丰收节的早晨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骆驼山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一峰永远的骆驼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远地沉默与奔走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从不留倒退的蹄印"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被风雨淋成一个警句"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装点着那片天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有声或无声的姿势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一种悲壮和歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一个民族心中矗立"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们感受真实的威严与自豪"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}